com.cubeia.firebase.api.game.table
Interface ExtendedDetailsProvider

public interface ExtendedDetailsProvider

Provides extended, game specific details for players and table. If needed this interface should be implemented by the game.

Method Summary
 List<Param> getExtendedDetails(Table table, int playerId, boolean fromLobby)
          Gets a map of details for a given player.
 

Method Detail

getExtendedDetails

List<Param> getExtendedDetails(Table table,
                               int playerId,
                               boolean fromLobby)
Gets a map of details for a given player. Should return a list of Params containing the details. The values can be either Strings or Integers. If details are requested for a player who cannot be located null can safely be returned.

Parameters:
table - the table where the player should be seated
playerId - the playerId to get details for
fromLobby - boolean indicating if the details are requested from the lobby or from within the game
Returns:
a List of parameters, or null if no details are available.
